---
---

<section class="km-section--deep relative overflow-hidden min-h-screen flex items-center">
  <div class="km-container relative z-10 pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-28">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-16">
      <!-- Left: Text -->
      <div class="lg:w-[58%] hero-stagger">
        <img src="/kubmin-logo.svg" alt="Kubmin" class="h-12 mb-8 block" />

        <span class="inline-flex items-center w-fit px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest bg-[#10b981]/8 text-[#10b981] border border-[#10b981]/15 mb-8">
          Beta — Free to Start
        </span>

        <h1 class="km-heading km-heading--display text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem)] mb-6 max-w-[620px]">
          Ship fast. But know what each deploy <span class="text-[#10b981]">costs in money and efficiency.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-[clamp(1rem,2vw,1.25rem)] text-[#10b981]/80 mb-5 max-w-[520px] leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Version 2.1 uses 30% more energy than 2.0. Your monitoring didn't catch that. Kubmin would have.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[15px] text-zinc-500 mb-10 max-w-[500px] leading-[1.7]">
          Per-workload efficiency tracking across deployments, automated waste detection, and ready-to-use kubectl fixes. The layer between your workloads and your cloud bill that's been missing.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <a href="https://kubmin.ksctl.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="km-cta">
            Start Free <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-[#10b981] transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-1.5">
            See how it works
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-600 tracking-wide max-w-[450px]">
          Built on Kepler (CNCF) &middot; SCI-aligned (Green Software Foundation) &middot; Powered by ksctl
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Hero image -->
      <div class="lg:w-[42%] mt-12 lg:mt-0 hero-screenshot relative">
        <div class="km-screenshot-glow">
          <div class="km-browser relative shadow-km-browser-hero">
            <div class="km-browser-bar">
              <span class="km-browser-dot bg-[#ff5f57]/80"></span>
              <span class="km-browser-dot bg-[#febc2e]/80"></span>
              <span class="km-browser-dot bg-[#28c840]/80"></span>
              <span class="ml-4 text-[11px] text-zinc-600 font-mono tracking-wide">kubmin.ksctl.com</span>
            </div>
            <img
              src="/kubmin/kubmin-workload-hero.png"
              alt="Kubmin dashboard showing workload cost, energy, and efficiency metrics"
              loading="eager"
              class="w-full block"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom fade into next section -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#111114] to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</section>
